videos.description: When Kimbal Mackenzie gives the Bison a dramatic 65-64 victory with a buzzer-beating 3, announcer Doug Birdsong provides a rather energetic call to match the enthusiasm of the fans rushing the court.
videos.headline: Bucknell announcer goes crazy after buzzer-beater
